{"title":"模范妇女  ——记傅家庄模范妇女小芹","authors":["钟铃"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"模范妇女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——记傅家庄模范妇女小芹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟铃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你劳动在谷堆里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披着谷皮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一锨一锨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"格朗格朗地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听起来是多有力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场上几个妇女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也跟你在一组；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象你一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愉快是你们大家的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁、耙、耩、锄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你都会做，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少小伙子都眼气；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好姑娘呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年才十七。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥参军去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹老了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘指望你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好军属，靠自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你学会了养种地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女互助组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你领导的；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你虽年青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她们都拥护你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你常跟大家说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱农民翻身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头一个靠共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再一个就靠生产！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你懂得了真理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女都跟你学习；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连那上年岁的老妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不喊你小芹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都称你模范妇女！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"—九月在南宫"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}